content:
Specify your trusted sites in the CRM Analytics allowlist. You can include embedded CRM Analytics dashboards in websites and apps outside of Salesforce servers.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To set up an Analytics allowlist, complete the following steps:

From Setup, enter Allowlist in the Quick Find box, then select Allowlist under Analytics.
On the Allowlist for Embedding Dashboards page, click New.
On the Allowed Site Edit page, enter the information for the site you want to add to the CRM Analytics allowlist.
Click Save.
title: Configuring CRM Analytics Allowlist
